  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "+/a9XmPwQixGFroME/GMEOLpReZZV4ARosR9orAplJY=",
    "originContent": "<p align=\"center\">",
    "translatedContent": "  বেথেসডাৰ দ্বাৰা Creation Kitৰ বাবে পৰিবৰ্তন, উন্নয়ন আৰু উল্টা-ইঞ্জিনিয়াৰ কৰা সম্পদৰ এক সংগ্ৰহ।"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "vemoBfiHcS9U4ZRggqjTr5jDfSkiRcTsy8JgtSUjrJE=",
    "originContent": "  A collection of modifications, enhancements, and reverse engineered resources for Creation Kit by Bethesda.",
    "translatedContent": "</p>"
