    "originContent": ">Check with Steam if your CPU support avx2. Open Steam, in left corner hover over help menu select System Information and search for AVX2.  ",
    "translatedContent": ">Steam ত চাওক আপোনাৰ CPU avx2 সমৰ্থন কৰে নে। Steam খোলক, বাওঁ কোণত help menu ত hover কৰি System Information বাছক আৰু AVX2 সন্ধান কৰক।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "zb/B/OHlKrfEqVkWygUjXGiFgd+pn6RgqXUh/jwMFyQ=",
    "originContent": ">If it is supported go with regular release  ",
    "translatedContent": ">যদি সমৰ্থন কৰে, regular মুক্তি লৈ যাওক  "
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "pKBHSP5zD1tpBVe3afVdTMVHYgNhtDpa/L85E7UMGgk=",
    "originContent": ">If it is not, go with noavx2 release  ",
    "translatedContent": ">যদি নকৰে, noavx2 মুক্তি লৈ যাওক  "
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "VcRLeaoeZLP2jNj2qTSBTq/hf2NipE0uvmuhROj9+jk=",
    "originContent": "### Fresh Install",
    "translatedContent": "### নতুন স্থাপন"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "FYbmzIzgKdQ/+LejqSqLMmplx4XgPVQDtGpyCq8sz4A=",
    "originContent": "Download any [supported game](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/wiki#brief) and install Creation Kit.  ",
    "translatedContent": "[সমৰ্থিত গেম](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/wiki#brief) যিকোনোখন ডাউনলোড কৰক আৰু Creation Kit স্থাপন কৰক।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "REwfufXhw9N8xChFtWed8nQErGsZ8tuO1tnRI/b39vA=",
    "originContent": "Download [latest release](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/releases) of **CKPE** for your game.  ",
    "translatedContent": "আপোনাৰ গেমৰ বাবে **CKPE** ৰ [নৱতম মুক্তি](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/releases) ডাউনলোড কৰক।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "UJRa7RW1zDt/LmLNhRDLWuxTSpo2lr5XWd2K42fK2Mg=",
    "originContent": "Extract all contents into game directory, so that **ckpe_loader.exe** is in the same folder as **CreationKit.exe**.",
    "translatedContent": "সমস্ত সামগ্রী গেম ডাইৰেক্টৰিত extract কৰক, যাতে **ckpe_loader.exe** **CreationKit.exe** ৰ সৈতে একে ফোল্ডাৰত থাকে।"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "ssSJAgg38PqeqMuiXawYsqaO0+hL0+Q/hRGHxsC844U=",
    "originContent": "### Update",
    "translatedContent": "### আপডেট"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "REwfufXhw9N8xChFtWed8nQErGsZ8tuO1tnRI/b39vA=",
    "originContent": "Download [latest release](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/releases) of **CKPE** for your game.  ",
    "translatedContent": "আপোনাৰ গেমৰ বাবে **CKPE** ৰ [নৱতম মুক্তি](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/releases) ডাউনলোড কৰক।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "Gyixvj4bgedGSkU9zGFahN8ZdzfsSfYe9VL+dguagLw=",
    "originContent": "Extract all contents into game directory, so that **ckpe_loader.exe** is in the same folder as **CreationKit.exe**.  ",
    "translatedContent": "সমস্ত সামগ্রী গেম ডাইৰেক্টৰিত extract কৰক, যাতে **ckpe_loader.exe** **CreationKit.exe** ৰ সৈতে একে ফোল্ডাৰত থাকে।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "Fa2pWqaDtAc+rgu1D7qD7EqoxgbFyvXzE2cAxdW+dc4=",
    "originContent": "Agree to replace all files.",
    "translatedContent": "সমস্ত ফাইল replace কৰিবলৈ সম্মতি দিয়ক।"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "6PpyEZNf51VxBE5HA/fAzzalKi5LUolsxDiKv1zlSRg=",
    "originContent": "### Compilation",
    "translatedContent": "### সংকলন"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "Un/saEFe4aD+Ia7QOBe+8xxIGWYo6CQXp3sgh56JGcw=",
    "originContent": "Regular users only need this method to access the newest features which haven't been released yet.  ",
    "translatedContent": "Regular ব্যৱহাৰকাৰীসকলক কেৱল এই পদ্ধতি ব্যৱহাৰ কৰিব লাগে নতুন ফিচাৰসমূহৰ বাবে যিবোৰ এতিয়াও মুক্তি হোৱা নাই।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "he2JOv0UU7O1Lou6hquY2qiuSHsMmnNrg1W0kt22eAg=",
    "originContent": "Open a project in **`Visual Studio 2022`** or later. Build the project in **`Release`** mode or **`Release-NoAVX2`**.  ",
    "translatedContent": "**`Visual Studio 2022`** বা তাৰ পিছৰ কোনো প্ৰকল্প খোলক। প্ৰকল্প **`Release`** বা **`Release-NoAVX2`** মোডত Build কৰক।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "o5d9gBXtEJs264cyeGixcmFpU+bHZNjvVQKjKP4IXrM=",
    "originContent": "Then move your build output into game directory, so that **ckpe_loader.exe** is in the same folder as **CreationKit.exe**.  ",
    "translatedContent": "তাতপিছত আপোনাৰ build output গেম ডাইরেক্টৰিত স্থানান্তৰ কৰক, যাতে **ckpe_loader.exe** **CreationKit.exe** ৰ সৈতে একে ফোল্ডাৰত থাকে।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "wlidYo4cVzV+VT7R4QCUaUGxSMdOsfQXvEgSbn5TaXY=",
    "originContent": "If you are asked to replace old files agree to replace all.",
    "translatedContent": "পুৰণি ফাইল replace কৰিবলৈ অনুরোধ কৰিলে, সমস্ত replace কৰিবলৈ সম্মতি দিয়ক।"
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "tQHzqK5najooR1VGD9f9x79667YopoeyFpJFE7OfkRc=",
    "originContent": "### Automate builds (Beta)",
    "translatedContent": "### স্বচালিত build (Beta)"
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "QiSo6Nxl9taRi26Y03lxv+7nJP5ObO+B/TIERl9ficg=",
    "originContent": "Download [latest commit build](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/actions) of **CKPE** for your game.  ",
    "translatedContent": "আপোনাৰ গেমৰ বাবে **CKPE** ৰ [নৱতম commit build](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/actions) ডাউনলোড কৰক।  "
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "Gyixvj4bgedGSkU9zGFahN8ZdzfsSfYe9VL+dguagLw=",
    "originContent": "Extract all contents into game directory, so that **ckpe_loader.exe** is in the same folder as **CreationKit.exe**.  ",
    "translatedContent": "সমস্ত সামগ্রী গেম ডাইৰেক্টৰিত extract কৰক, যাতে **ckpe_loader.exe** **CreationKit.exe** ৰ সৈতে একে ফোল্ডাৰত থাকে।  "
  },
